name: Dice Ibegon
Lore: 'Female companion of Lak Sivrak. A Florn lamproid. Dangerous predator with a poison stinger. Rumored to have mysterious time-shifting attunement to the Force.',
Text: 'If present where an opponent''s character just fired a weapon, may use 1 Force to utilize Dice''s poison stinger (once per turn). Target that character and draw destiny. If destiny = ability, target is ''hit''.',
